vip.can_email_notification1: Bind the mailbox, you can choose the important information that needs to be sent, so that you will not miss any prompt.
vip.can_exclusive_customer_service1: We provide a 7*24-hour exclusive customer service manager for senior VIP members to solve all problems for members.
vip.can_leveraged_investment1: Open the leverage, the upper limit is 125X, the annual rate of return reaches 1250%, and the wealth password is quickly opened.
vip.can_pm_friends1: Members can send private messages to designated members through the system's message.
vip.can_prevent_liquidation1: When the market triggers liquidation, the loyalty value will be automatically retrieved to make up the position to prevent liquidation from occurring.
vip.can_profit_guarantee1: When the profit is lower than APY5%, it will automatically make up the profit to ensure the minimum profit.
vip.can_promotion_first_notice1: When high-yield and quota-limited activities, it will be pushed to higher-level members first.

vip.can_trail_bonus1: All certified members can receive a $10,000 trial bonus and can withdraw profits for three days.
vip.can_view_contact_details1: Members can view the contact information of each other's social software and find each other through social software.
vip.daily_referral_rewards1: Daily referral bonus. If the number of referrals exceeds the number of daily referrals, there will be no corresponding commission. Recommend 1 person 10USDC.
vip.level_1_refer1: For first-level referrals, you will get a percentage of his daily earnings.
vip.level_2_refer1: For second-level referrals, you will receive a percentage of his daily earnings.
vip.level_3_refer1: For third-level referrals, you will receive a percentage of his daily earnings.
vip.leveraged_investment1: The leverage multiples that can be opened for each level are different. The higher the leverage, the higher the income.
vip.loan_charges1: The fee for the loan is based on the percentage of your current income. The higher the level, the lower the cost of the loan.
vip.max_staking_term1: The longer the staking term is set, the more profit and the higher the stability will be obtained.
vip.minimum_apy_guarantee1: When the income is less than the minimum guarantee, AI Earn will automatically make up the income, and the higher the level, the higher the guaranteed APY.
vip.need_withdrawal_verification1: In order to ensure that all members' activities are carried out in the Coinbase wallet, vip0 members need to verify the wallet balance when making withdrawal, and the maximum amount of payment = wallet balance.
vip.network_fee1: Every transaction in Ethereum needs to deduct network fees. Depending on the membership level, we will deduct some of the fees.
vip.number_of_withdrawals1: Limit on the number of daily withdrawals.
vip.withdrawal_time1: T + 1 refers to applying for withdrawal, the money will arrive on the next day, T + 0 refers to applying for withdrawal, and the money will arrive on the same day.
